Description: We are a crowdfunding platform for the part-time creator. It's the way budding creators get fan support in return for digital collectibles.
Full Description: Less than 4% of creators on social are full-time creators. Yet, nearly 100% of the monetization platforms are built for this audience so that they can make a living. For the part-time creator (with a full-time job), paying the bills is not the primary need for monetization. Rather, it's the funding of their "passion project" that often is money constrained. The current platforms require exclusive content to be effective at monetization. For part-time creators, it is nearly impossible to create any additional content in the little time that they have. Our solution is specifically designed for the part-time creator. Instead of a place where creators have to spend long hours creating exclusive content, we've created a place for creators to mint exclusive digital collectibles (NFTs) for fans that support their work in minutes. Fans like it because they've helped their favorite creator, and added a unique piece to their growing collection of digital collectibles on Back My Hobby.
